<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM2.2.10">
<l>kaḷvā vemmaiyu mēḻu lakuni</l>
<l>ṉuḷḷē tōṟṟiya viṟaiva veṉṟu</l>
<l>veḷḷēṟa ṉāṉmuka ṉintiraṉ vāṉavar</l>
<l>puḷḷūr tikaḻal paṇintēt tuvarē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Saying “o robber, lord who made appear inside</l>
<l>yourself both us and the seven worlds”,</l>
<l>the one on the white bull the one with four faces, Indra [and] the celestials</l>
<l>humbly praise the anklet[ted feet] of [him on] the bird vehicle.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
